    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "It could be (in theory) but the string in your example is not a UTF-8 encoded String.  It is a URL-encoded ASCII string.  Hence the title is misleading."
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 47283,
