    "post_id" : 6138127,
    "comment_id" : 7125923,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "It is also worth noting that all the characters in the <code>url</code> string are ASCII, and this is also true after the string has been URL decoded.  <code>&#39;%&#39;</code> is an ASCII char and <code>%xx</code> represents an ASCII char if <code>xx</code> is less than (hexadecimal) <code>80</code>."
  } ],
