    "body" : "<p><code>%3A</code> and <code>%2F</code> are URL encoded characters. Use this java code to convert them back into <code>:</code> and <code>/</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>String decoded = java.net.URLDecoder.decode(url, \"UTF-8\");\n</code></pre>\n"
